Package main.model

Interface Displayable

All Known Subinterfaces:
Request
All Known Implementing Classes:
Camp, Enquiry, Suggestion
public interface Displayable
An interface representing objects that can be displayed in a formatted manner. Classes implementing this interface provide methods to generate string representations suitable for display in the user interface. The methods include variations for displaying objects with or without a specified type.
